        <h1>Leading the way in the Digital Market</h1>

<h3>40 Years as a Partner to Publishers</h3>
<p>With Ingram there is no fear of being left behind by new technology.  Publishers can be confident  knowing our solutions provide secure, cutting-edge, and profitable answers to the questions they have about the changing opportunities in the market.  Maximizing publishers’ profit is our primary goal. 
</p>

<h3>Ingram has solutions for every publisher’s needs</h3>
<ul>
 <li>
     Secure digital warehousing 
 </li>

 <li>
     Distribution to all channels
 </li>

 <li>
     Content repurposed for multiple devices
 </li>

 <li>
     Tools for marketing &amp; promoting content<br />

 </li>
</ul>

<h3>And through our sister content companies...</h3>
<ul>
 <li>
     Print-on-demand
 </li>

 <li>
     Print distribution  <br />
<br>
 </li>
</ul>
<p><div class="icon-text-small">
   <a href="http://www.ingramdigital.com/publishers/coresource" title="Content Solutions"><img src="/static/images/layout/icon_publisher_large.jpg" alt="CoreSource"></a> 
</p>

<h2>Content Solutions</h2>
<p>Ingram's CoreSource lets publishers explore new opportunities with easy, automated solutions to manage content logistics with any business partner.  Publishers can use CoreSource to store images, print and print-on-demand files, e-books, audio books, XML, video and Flash content. Once a file is available in CoreSource it can be made ready to deliver in a wide range of formats.
</p>
<p><a href="/publishers/coresource/">Learn more</a>
</p>
<p><span class="clear">&nbsp;</span></div>
</p>
<p><div class="icon-text-small">
   <a href="http://www.ingramdigital.com/publishers/libraries" title="Library Solutions"><img src="/static/images/layout/icon_library_large.jpg" alt="Libraries" /></a>
</p>

<h2>Library Solutions</h2>
<p>Ingram Digital provides publishers with digital content delivery to libraries and institutions worldwide through our MyiLibrary platform. We’re already providing public, academic and professional libraries with over 230,000 titles and 8,000+ downloadable audio titles from the top global publishers. 
</p>
<p><a href="/publishers/libraries/">Learn more</a>
</p>
<p><span class="clear">&nbsp;</span></div>
</p>
<p><div class="icon-text-small">
   <a href="http://www.ingramdigital.com/publishers/education" title="Education Solutions"><img src="/static/images/layout/icon_education_large.jpg" alt="VitalSource" /></a>
</p>

<h2>Education Solutions</h2>
<p>Expand your options to deliver your content using the leading interactive format for education. <a href="/education/students/">VitalSource Bookshelf®</a> was developed by educators specifically for textbooks and learning materials -- it includes a powerful set of built-in tools to make content engaging, interactive and in tune with the needs of today's students.  Publish new content or repurpose current content with options for embedded multimedia, chapterization, or bundling.
</p>
<p><a href="/publishers/education/">Learn more</a>
</p>
<p><span class="clear">&nbsp;</span></div>
</p>
<p><div class="icon-text-small">
   <a href="http://www.ingramdigital.com/publishers/retailer" title="Retail Solutions"><img src="/static/images/layout/icon_retail_large.jpg" alt="Education" /></a>
</p>

<h2>Retail Solutions</h2>
<p>Do more with your content. Take advantage of fast growing digital sales channels with Ingram Digital Retail Solutions.  We provide the tools to help publishers maximize market exposure and revenue opportunities -- safe, secure solutions to enable your digital strategy.<br />

</p>
<p><a href="/publishers/retailer/">Learn more</a>
</p>
<p><span class="clear">&nbsp;</span></div>
</p>
    </div>

            
            
